pma:database.pma:table: CREATE TABLE `Casting` ( `MovieID` int(11) NOT NULL, `ActorID` int(11) NOT NULL, `Ordinal` int(11) NOT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`MovieID`,`ActorID`), KEY `ActorID` (`ActorID`), CONSTRAINT `Casting_ibfk_1` FOREIGN KEY (`MovieID`) REFERENCES `Movie` (`MovieID`), CONSTRAINT `Casting_ibfk_2` FOREIGN KEY (`ActorID`) REFERENCES `Actor` (`ActorID`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=latin1;

CREATE TABLE `Comments` ( `CommentID` int(100) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `MovieID` int(11) NOT NULL, `Login` varchar(20) NOT NULL, `Comment` varchar(300) NOT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`CommentID`,`MovieID`), KEY `fk_MovieID_Comment` (`MovieID`), CONSTRAINT `fk_MovieID_Comment` FOREIGN KEY (`MovieID`) REFERENCES `Movie` (`MovieID`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=15 DEFAULT CHARSET=latin1;

CREATE TABLE `Movie` ( `MovieID` int(11) NOT NULL, `Titre` varchar(70) NOT NULL, `Année` int(4) NOT NULL, `Score` float NOT NULL, `Votes` int(11) NOT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`MovieID`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=latin1;

CREATE TABLE `Utilisateur` ( `UserID` int(11) NOT NULL, `Login` varchar(20) NOT NULL, `Pass` varchar(255) NOT NULL, `Nom` varchar(35) NOT NULL, `Mail` varchar(35) NOT NULL, `image` tinyint(1) NOT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`UserID`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=latin1;

CREATE TABLE `Vote` ( `MovieID` int(11) NOT NULL, `UserID` int(11) NOT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`MovieID`,`UserID`), KEY `fk_UserID` (`UserID`), CONSTRAINT `fk_MovieID` FOREIGN KEY (`MovieID`) REFERENCES `Movie` (`MovieID`), CONSTRAINT `fk_UserID` FOREIGN KEY (`UserID`) REFERENCES `Utilisateur` (`UserID`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=latin1;
